      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>I'm not sure I can take a \"break.\" It's not like I can just go on vacation and come back to a new life. Everything is so loud and heavy and the pressure to perform is constant. Even when I'm sitting still, I'm thinking about how much I've failed. It's not just a setback, it feels like the end of the road. I'm just so done with the constant struggle to stay afloat. I just want the noise to be gone. I just want some actual peace.",
